Package: emilyos
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Emily Springerton <emilyspringerton@gmail.com>
Depends: systemd
Description: EmilyOS policy kernel
 A Linux-based operating environment implementing posture-gated sessions,
 capability-checked agency verbs, tamper-evident audit logging, and SOC 2
 Type II-ready controls. The policy kernel that enforces deliberate, auditable
 interaction on Linux.
